### Course Management API - Test Requests
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health HTTP/1.1

###

### 1. Create a New Course
POST http://localhost:3000/api/courses HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Complete Node.js Developer Course",
  "description": "Learn Node.js by building real-world applications with Node, Express, MongoDB, and more",
  "instructor": "John Doe",
  "duration": 40,
  "price": 99.99,
  "category": "Programming",
  "level": "intermediate"
}

###

